{"video_id": "3N84GvoFdBY", "title": "Four Golden Secrets of Soulful Japa| Sri Madhu Pandit Dasa | Ekadashi Soulful Japa Training", "speaker": "HG Madhu Pandit Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3N84GvoFdBY", "duration": 1844, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 10.34, "text": " Many times I have given summary talk on soulful japa."}, {"start": 13.68, "end": 24.740000000000002, "text": " So now onwards on our ekadashi, I will deal with the cards, the cue cards that we have made."}, {"start": 24.740000000000002, "end": 35.56, "text": " These cue cards are how best to utilize these cue cards."}, {"start": 35.56, "end": 47.24, "text": " These cue cards are ultimately the content in these cue cards,"}, {"start": 47.24, "end": 54.68000000000001, "text": " the intellectual content,"}, {"start": 54.68000000000001, "end": 54.72, "text": " the intellectual content,"}, {"start": 54.72, "end": 54.74, "text": " the intellectual content,"}, {"start": 54.74, "end": 56.68, "text": " the spiritual content,"}, {"start": 56.68, "end": 65.78, "text": " the emotional content has to enter our subconscious mind"}, {"start": 65.78, "end": 74.64, "text": " by repeated reflection and contemplation."}, {"start": 74.64, "end": 82.80000000000001, "text": " Once it enters our subconscious,"}, {"start": 82.80000000000001, "end": 84.72, "text": " then it creates a wonderful,"}, {"start": 84.72, "end": 91.76, "text": " wonderful background to our chanting and hearing in the foreground."}, {"start": 91.76, "end": 95.76, "text": " The foreground mind will be chanting and hearing and tasking."}, {"start": 95.76, "end": 109.75999999999999, "text": " The background mind will be relating with the nama prabhu who is before us."}, {"start": 109.75999999999999, "end": 113.75999999999999, "text": " This is the basic premise of nama prabhu."}, {"start": 113.75999999999999, "end": 114.7, "text": " This is the basic premise of nama prabhu."}, {"start": 114.7, "end": 115.58, "text": " This is the basic premise of nama prabhu."}, {"start": 115.58, "end": 118.58, "text": " Soulful japa."}, {"start": 118.58, "end": 123.74000000000001, "text": " Soulful japa means whole mind japa."}, {"start": 123.74000000000001, "end": 125.74000000000001, "text": " Both foreground mind and background mind."}, {"start": 125.74000000000001, "end": 128.3, "text": " Both foreground mind and background mind."}, {"start": 128.3, "end": 133.3, "text": " Then there is complete absorption in nama prabhu."}, {"start": 133.3, "end": 139.06, "text": " Our full mind is foreground mind and background mind."}, {"start": 139.06, "end": 139.74, "text": " So we should train our mind."}, {"start": 139.74, "end": 144.68, "text": " So we should train our mind."}, {"start": 144.68, "end": 149.68, "text": " Not only in foreground chanting and hearing,"}, {"start": 149.68, "end": 159.68, "text": " but also train the mind in background mind"}, {"start": 159.68, "end": 165.68, "text": " to have only matters which are glories of the holy name,"}, {"start": 165.68, "end": 172.68, "text": " matters which are feelings about the relationship with the holy name,"}, {"start": 172.68, "end": 174.56, "text": " the bhavanas,"}, {"start": 174.56, "end": 175.56, "text": " the feelings about the holy name."}, {"start": 175.56, "end": 189.56, "text": " So that part of the training is what is designed through these cards."}, {"start": 189.56, "end": 196.56, "text": " These are all manifestations from Srila Prabhupada and nama prabhu, these cards."}, {"start": 196.56, "end": 201.56, "text": " These are all manifestations from Srila Prabhupada and nama prabhu, these cards."}, {"start": 201.56, "end": 202.56, "text": " It has very deep meaning."}, {"start": 202.56, "end": 203.56, "text": " It has very deep meaning."}, {"start": 203.56, "end": 208.56, "text": " It has very deep meaning."}, {"start": 208.56, "end": 212.56, "text": " It has very deep meaning."}, {"start": 212.56, "end": 217.56, "text": " Ultimately our mind,"}, {"start": 217.56, "end": 223.56, "text": " there are three stages of perfecting japa."}, {"start": 223.56, "end": 225.56, "text": " Mindful japa,"}, {"start": 225.56, "end": 226.56, "text": " Spiritful japa,"}, {"start": 226.56, "end": 231.56, "text": " and Soulful japa."}, {"start": 231.56, "end": 238.56, "text": " Mindful japa is when you give your complete mind to chanting and hearing,"}, {"start": 238.56, "end": 240.56, "text": " chanting and hearing,"}, {"start": 240.56, "end": 244.56, "text": " and feeling his presence in the background mind,"}, {"start": 244.56, "end": 251.56, "text": " nama prabhu's presence."}, {"start": 251.56, "end": 259.56, "text": " In other words, chanting and hearing and tasking with shraddha is mindful japa."}, {"start": 259.56, "end": 264.56, "text": " in other words, chanting and hearing and tasking with shraddha is mindful japa."}, {"start": 264.56, "end": 265.56, "text": " Then,"}, {"start": 265.56, "end": 266.56, "text": " Spiritful japa."}, {"start": 266.56, "end": 271.56, "text": " Spiritful japa means not only mind,"}, {"start": 271.56, "end": 276.56, "text": " you chant with joy, excitement, enthusiasm,"}, {"start": 276.56, "end": 283.56, "text": " you chant with joy, excitement, enthusiasm,"}, {"start": 283.56, "end": 284.56, "text": " heart beat."}, {"start": 284.56, "end": 286.56, "text": " heart beat."}, {"start": 286.56, "end": 287.56, "text": " Heart beat."}, {"start": 287.56, "end": 288.56, "text": " Heart beat."}, {"start": 288.56, "end": 306.08, "text": " heartfully, liking to chant. So mindful chanting, mindful japa plus preeti, aglada,"}, {"start": 306.08, "end": 316.3, "text": " hrstam, utsaha, these are all, you know, you have to offer from your spirit. You"}, {"start": 316.3, "end": 324.06, "text": " have to be happy about chanting. You have to be enthusiastic about chanting. You have"}, {"start": 324.06, "end": 341.18, "text": " to joyfully chant, happily chant, enthusiastically repeat. These are all feelings, enthusiasm,"}, {"start": 341.18, "end": 346.28000000000003, "text": " joy, happily doing."}, {"start": 346.28000000000003, "end": 357.50000000000006, "text": " Which means this comes from the spirit. Mindful japa is more like controlling your mind. It"}, {"start": 357.50000000000006, "end": 364.34000000000003, "text": " s a technique. Don t go here in their mind, only here. That is mindful japa. Spiritful"}, {"start": 364.34000000000003, "end": 375.40000000000003, "text": " japa means you start giving your spirit. Then soulful japa means chanting in relation to"}, {"start": 375.40000000000003, "end": 376.26000000000005, "text": " the mind. So, this is the spiritual japa. This is the spiritual japa. This is the spiritual"}, {"start": 376.28000000000003, "end": 388.52000000000004, "text": " relationship with the holy name. Like sambandha, saranagati, kripapeksha, it is like talking"}, {"start": 388.52000000000004, "end": 401.58000000000004, "text": " to the Nama Prabhu. Kripapeksha, vinamrtha, all these other cards up to sixteen cards."}, {"start": 406.28000000000003, "end": 421.04, "text": " So, the essence of all this is in the golden command. So, today let us just go through"}, {"start": 421.04, "end": 429.16, "text": " the golden command so that you get familiarized with this card. This one card hundred times"}, {"start": 429.16, "end": 434.16, "text": " you should read, think, contemplate, reflect intellectually, physically, mentally, mentally,"}, {"start": 434.16, "end": 435.64000000000004, "text": " physically and physically. This is the golden command. This is the golden command. So, let"}, {"start": 435.64, "end": 446.15999999999997, "text": " intellectually, contemplate emotionally, then it will enter your subconscious mind."}, {"start": 446.16, "end": 466.18, "text": " Now the golden secrets cue card, the three golden secrets of soulful japa."}, {"start": 466.18, "end": 476.14000000000004, "text": " The first secret, hear what you chant without thinking activity."}, {"start": 476.14, "end": 485.9, "text": " Chant Hare Krishna, exactly same sound you hear."}, {"start": 485.9, "end": 490.71999999999997, "text": " Chanting is crying to Namaprabhu to descend."}, {"start": 490.71999999999997, "end": 502.38, "text": " And hearing is embracing the descended Krishna's sound persona respectfully."}, {"start": 502.38, "end": 506.12, "text": " Hear what you chant without any thinking activity."}, {"start": 506.12, "end": 519.38, "text": " Because if you do thinking activity, you cannot hear, hearing is very important."}, {"start": 519.38, "end": 529.92, "text": " Even if the thinking activity is about the philosophy of Krishna consciousness, no, hear."}, {"start": 529.92, "end": 535.92, "text": " If you are thinking of the philosophy of Krishna consciousness, then you are not hearing."}, {"start": 536.12, "end": 545.94, "text": " Krishna is come before you know want to be heard."}, {"start": 545.94, "end": 554.5600000000001, "text": " So that the golden command of Srila Prabhupada, Chant Hare Krishna, and exactly the same sound"}, {"start": 554.5600000000001, "end": 561.04, "text": " you hear."}, {"start": 561.04, "end": 563.12, "text": " And chanting is crying to Namaprabhu from your heart."}, {"start": 563.12, "end": 564.12, "text": " And listening is coming at you."}, {"start": 564.12, "end": 565.12, "text": " We have to listen, chase with our eyes and distorted space of mind."}, {"start": 565.12, "end": 566.12, "text": " Do not forget the singing."}, {"start": 566.12, "end": 583.12, "text": " Chanting should be crying from the heart. To whom? To Krishna. Please come down. I need"}, {"start": 583.12, "end": 594.5600000000001, "text": " your association. And then hearing is to embrace Krishna's sound persona who has come before"}, {"start": 594.5600000000001, "end": 606.1600000000001, "text": " me respectfully. Krishna is within and without of everything. Any devotee who cryingly chants,"}, {"start": 606.1600000000001, "end": 620.0600000000001, "text": " Lord is on his tongue for sure, 100%. Mechanically chanting, you should cryingly chant."}, {"start": 624.5600000000001, "end": 636.0400000000001, "text": " If you are materially satisfied, you cannot cry. Your heart cannot cry. You feel everything"}, {"start": 636.0400000000001, "end": 652.22, "text": " nicely settled, your heart cannot cry. And then this understanding has to be there to"}, {"start": 652.22, "end": 653.22, "text": " hear."}, {"start": 653.22, "end": 665.02, "text": " your soul is touching Krishna who has come. That is the only way for us to get sacchidanandaized"}, {"start": 665.02, "end": 675.46, "text": " or develop the same quality as Krishna. So that is the first secret. Chant. First secret"}, {"start": 675.46, "end": 687.6, "text": " is hear what you chant. Second secret, task hearing over previous hearing. One mantra"}, {"start": 687.6, "end": 701.0600000000001, "text": " hearing is over. Before its effect is over, put on the next one. That means you pile up."}, {"start": 701.0600000000001, "end": 705.44, "text": " You should not be in between the mantras, something else."}, {"start": 705.44, "end": 713.4200000000001, "text": " You should not think. Your attention should be piling up one hearing over another hearing."}, {"start": 713.4200000000001, "end": 719.0, "text": " That can happen only if you do that work, tasking. Tasking means it is a work."}, {"start": 719.0, "end": 726.2, "text": " Hare Krishna Hare Krishna Krishna Krishna Hare Hare Hare Rama Hare Rama eva rang"}, {"start": 726.2, "end": 734.62, "text": " tut in tasking next, put the next one on top. Here one after the other and here one after"}, {"start": 734.62, "end": 734.82, "text": " the other."}, {"start": 734.82, "end": 734.8800000000001, "text": " One after the other."}, {"start": 734.8800000000001, "end": 735.0, "text": " Here one after the other."}, {"start": 735.0, "end": 735.0600000000001, "text": " One after the other."}, {"start": 735.0600000000001, "end": 735.1, "text": " Here one after the other."}, {"start": 735.1, "end": 735.4200000000001, "text": " Here one after the other."}, {"start": 735.42, "end": 758.0, "text": " the other, build up. One Hare Krishna chanting you do, that association, let's say it gives"}, {"start": 758.0, "end": 768.24, "text": " you some warmth. It's energy. Before that cools off, next one should be there. Before"}, {"start": 768.24, "end": 777.72, "text": " that next one, before. Suppose you take a piece of iron, put in the fire, becomes heated,"}, {"start": 777.72, "end": 787.58, "text": " you take it out. It will become cool. Again you put it inside, it will become hot. Again"}, {"start": 787.58, "end": 787.98, "text": " you take it out."}, {"start": 788.0, "end": 793.18, "text": " Put it outside, become cool. But you keep it inside only, what will happen? Heat will"}, {"start": 793.18, "end": 799.12, "text": " build up, build up, build up. That is what meaning, task, hearing over previous hearing."}, {"start": 799.64, "end": 807.18, "text": " Hearing over previous hearing. This will ensure that no thinking activity will happen. Offer"}, {"start": 807.18, "end": 817.58, "text": " tasking of hearing as a doing, Ejna. This is an Ejna. It is pleasing to Krishna, this"}, {"start": 817.58, "end": 826.26, "text": " is a offering to Krishna. This is a giving and receiving. So if someone wants to go there,"}, {"start": 826.26, "end": 833.4200000000001, "text": " he will be heard. That is all. But you have to—î get the gift of hearing. Pay attention"}, {"start": 833.4200000000001, "end": 841.6, "text": " to this. Ejna. Doesn't mean, someone has to take your hand, but do you have to be careful"}, {"start": 841.6, "end": 842.5600000000001, "text": " about this?"}, {"start": 842.5600000000001, "end": 842.96, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 842.96, "end": 843.22, "text": " Ejna?"}, {"start": 843.22, "end": 843.3000000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 843.3000000000001, "end": 843.6400000000001, "text": " Ejna?"}, {"start": 843.6400000000001, "end": 843.76, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 843.76, "end": 844.22, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 844.22, "end": 844.46, "text": " Ejna!"}, {"start": 844.46, "end": 844.5200000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 844.5200000000001, "end": 844.6800000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 844.6800000000001, "end": 844.8000000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 844.8000000000001, "end": 845.1, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 845.1, "end": 845.2, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 845.2, "end": 845.22, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 845.22, "end": 845.5400000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 845.5400000000001, "end": 845.62, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 845.62, "end": 845.72, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 845.72, "end": 845.8000000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 845.8000000000001, "end": 846.24, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 846.24, "end": 846.58, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 846.58, "end": 846.7, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 846.7, "end": 847.0400000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 847.0400000000001, "end": 847.1600000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 847.1600000000001, "end": 847.1800000000001, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 847.1800000000001, "end": 847.26, "text": " Ejna."}, {"start": 847.26, "end": 861.26, "text": " Your chanting, your foreground mind, your background mind should be indulging in heart talk."}, {"start": 861.26, "end": 872.26, "text": " Heart talk about the glories of the holy name or heart talk about my relationship with Nama Prabhu."}, {"start": 872.26, "end": 881.26, "text": " Heart talk is another word for Bhavana."}, {"start": 881.26, "end": 891.26, "text": " Bhavana does not mean feeling alone."}, {"start": 891.26, "end": 895.26, "text": " Bhavana is a thought feeling."}, {"start": 895.26, "end": 901.26, "text": " Behind the feeling there is a thought."}, {"start": 901.26, "end": 905.26, "text": " A thought you are convinced about."}, {"start": 905.26, "end": 909.26, "text": " A belief is there."}, {"start": 909.26, "end": 916.26, "text": " And then the feeling is there."}, {"start": 916.26, "end": 927.26, "text": " Shraddha is a Bhavana, is a heart talk."}, {"start": 927.26, "end": 931.26, "text": " Just like you say, okay, you offer Shraddha to Nama Prabhu."}, {"start": 931.26, "end": 934.26, "text": " Then you explain, what is more?"}, {"start": 934.26, "end": 935.26, "text": " What is this?"}, {"start": 935.26, "end": 937.26, "text": " How do I offer Shraddha?"}, {"start": 937.26, "end": 939.26, "text": " Shraddha is a heart talk."}, {"start": 939.26, "end": 949.26, "text": " Heart talk is feelingly the narrative that Krishna is present before me."}, {"start": 949.26, "end": 950.26, "text": " Read the first line."}, {"start": 950.26, "end": 958.26, "text": " Offer in the background mind my emotionalized TRP narratives called Bhavana."}, {"start": 958.26, "end": 960.26, "text": " What is TRP?"}, {"start": 960.26, "end": 964.26, "text": " Truth, relationship and purpose."}, {"start": 964.26, "end": 966.26, "text": " We will explain what?"}, {"start": 966.26, "end": 969.26, "text": " Bhavana or heart talks."}, {"start": 969.26, "end": 972.26, "text": " Truth narrative is during japa."}, {"start": 972.26, "end": 976.26, "text": " Truth narrative is called Shraddha."}, {"start": 976.26, "end": 984.26, "text": " Shraddha that Krishna himself has incarnated before me on each bead as his persona of Shakti Avesha Nama."}, {"start": 984.26, "end": 986.26, "text": " See Nama Prabhu."}, {"start": 986.26, "end": 989.26, "text": " This is a simple matter of fact."}, {"start": 990.26, "end": 992.26, "text": " Faith."}, {"start": 992.26, "end": 994.26, "text": " Matter of truth."}, {"start": 994.26, "end": 995.26, "text": " Absolute truth."}, {"start": 995.26, "end": 1006.26, "text": " As soon as I am chanting Krishna who is within and without of everything is come before me as the hearable, chantable sound."}, {"start": 1006.26, "end": 1008.26, "text": " Is manifest."}, {"start": 1008.26, "end": 1009.26, "text": " Is pratyeksha."}, {"start": 1009.26, "end": 1012.26, "text": " Immediately."}, {"start": 1012.26, "end": 1018.26, "text": " So that truth, that feeling is called Shraddha."}, {"start": 1018.26, "end": 1023.26, "text": " Shraddha is fundamental."}, {"start": 1023.26, "end": 1025.26, "text": " Any other Bhavana is not there also."}, {"start": 1025.26, "end": 1027.26, "text": " Shraddha is fundamental."}, {"start": 1027.26, "end": 1036.26, "text": " That is why I said even in mindful chanting Shraddha is a must."}, {"start": 1036.26, "end": 1042.26, "text": " Without Shraddha mindful chanting is like a mechanical chant."}, {"start": 1042.26, "end": 1046.26, "text": " Mechanically you may hear every word that you are chanting."}, {"start": 1046.26, "end": 1049.26, "text": " Because of the mind control."}, {"start": 1049.26, "end": 1053.26, "text": " You control the mind that each sound is captured."}, {"start": 1053.26, "end": 1060.26, "text": " But Shraddha, why each sound you should take inside because he is Krishna himself has come before me."}, {"start": 1060.26, "end": 1064.26, "text": " That is Shraddha."}, {"start": 1064.26, "end": 1068.26, "text": " So that is a heart talk."}, {"start": 1068.26, "end": 1071.26, "text": " Shraddha is a heart talk."}, {"start": 1071.26, "end": 1075.26, "text": " See the soul in this material world in this body."}, {"start": 1075.26, "end": 1077.26, "text": " Trapped in this material world."}, {"start": 1077.26, "end": 1080.26, "text": " Trapped as in Indra."}, {"start": 1080.26, "end": 1094.26, "text": " One of the faculties that the soul, even now most powerful faculty of the soul is its ability to talk."}, {"start": 1094.26, "end": 1097.26, "text": " Remember that."}, {"start": 1097.26, "end": 1102.26, "text": " Not ability to think, not ability to see, it is ability to talk."}, {"start": 1102.26, "end": 1104.26, "text": " So spiritual life is all about Shraddha."}, {"start": 1104.26, "end": 1109.26, "text": " It is about talk."}, {"start": 1109.26, "end": 1112.26, "text": " Your mind immediately aligns with the talk."}, {"start": 1112.26, "end": 1116.26, "text": " Narrative."}, {"start": 1116.26, "end": 1118.26, "text": " That is why I call this as narrative."}, {"start": 1118.26, "end": 1125.26, "text": " Bhavana is nothing but emotionalized and intellectualized narrative."}, {"start": 1125.26, "end": 1128.26, "text": " Narrative of something you are convinced about."}, {"start": 1134.26, "end": 1138.26, "text": " So that is Shraddha."}, {"start": 1138.26, "end": 1140.26, "text": " So there is a narrative of truth."}, {"start": 1140.26, "end": 1142.26, "text": " There is a narrative of relationship."}, {"start": 1142.26, "end": 1148.26, "text": " What is my relationship with Nama?"}, {"start": 1148.26, "end": 1152.26, "text": " That narrative is Preeti."}, {"start": 1152.26, "end": 1158.26, "text": " Of respectful intimacy towards him."}, {"start": 1158.26, "end": 1160.26, "text": " That is a relationship."}, {"start": 1164.26, "end": 1169.26, "text": " That is also a originate."}, {"start": 1169.26, "end": 1173.26, "text": " It originates in a sound of the soul."}, {"start": 1173.26, "end": 1175.26, "text": " In talk of the soul."}, {"start": 1175.26, "end": 1180.26, "text": " Heart talk."}, {"start": 1180.26, "end": 1184.26, "text": " Vajatam Preeti Purvakam."}, {"start": 1184.26, "end": 1192.26, "text": " Preeti is a thought feeling."}, {"start": 1192.26, "end": 1195.26, "text": " Both intellectually, emotionally."}, {"start": 1195.26, "end": 1197.26, "text": " It has to be fed into your subconscious."}, {"start": 1197.26, "end": 1199.26, "text": " Through your conscious mind."}, {"start": 1199.26, "end": 1202.26, "text": " By repeatedly contemplating on it."}, {"start": 1202.26, "end": 1206.26, "text": " Reflecting on it."}, {"start": 1206.26, "end": 1213.26, "text": " How there is no one who loves me more than Krishna."}, {"start": 1213.26, "end": 1219.26, "text": " Krishna loves all living entities."}, {"start": 1222.26, "end": 1226.26, "text": " Therefore it is natural for me to love him."}, {"start": 1226.26, "end": 1228.26, "text": " To offer love to him."}, {"start": 1228.26, "end": 1230.26, "text": " Preeti."}, {"start": 1230.26, "end": 1233.26, "text": " I have Preeti towards Nama Prabhu."}, {"start": 1233.26, "end": 1235.26, "text": " I have Preeti towards Krishna."}, {"start": 1235.26, "end": 1237.26, "text": " Who is so kind and mercifully coming before me."}, {"start": 1237.26, "end": 1240.26, "text": " As his Shabda persona."}, {"start": 1240.26, "end": 1246.26, "text": " As his Nama persona."}, {"start": 1246.26, "end": 1249.26, "text": " So little intellectualizing is required."}, {"start": 1249.26, "end": 1251.26, "text": " So little intellectualizing is required."}, {"start": 1251.26, "end": 1255.26, "text": " Why I should have Preeti?"}, {"start": 1255.26, "end": 1264.26, "text": " That is intellectualization."}, {"start": 1264.26, "end": 1270.26, "text": " So in order to put any bhavana into your heart."}, {"start": 1270.26, "end": 1278.26, "text": " You have to be convinced."}, {"start": 1278.26, "end": 1280.26, "text": " A strong belief."}, {"start": 1280.26, "end": 1285.26, "text": " A strong belief of truth has to be there."}, {"start": 1285.26, "end": 1294.26, "text": " A strong belief of my relationship with Nama Prabhu."}, {"start": 1294.26, "end": 1297.26, "text": " So truth narrative of Nama Prabhu."}, {"start": 1297.26, "end": 1301.26, "text": " Relationship narrative of Nama Prabhu."}, {"start": 1301.26, "end": 1305.26, "text": " And then there is purpose."}, {"start": 1305.26, "end": 1306.26, "text": " The purpose is."}, {"start": 1306.26, "end": 1309.26, "text": " My purpose narrative is."}, {"start": 1309.26, "end": 1311.26, "text": " Loving him."}, {"start": 1311.26, "end": 1313.26, "text": " And receiving his Satchidananda association."}, {"start": 1313.26, "end": 1319.26, "text": " To awaken my love for him."}, {"start": 1319.26, "end": 1322.26, "text": " So this is the fundamental."}, {"start": 1322.26, "end": 1327.26, "text": " Shraddha and Preeti."}, {"start": 1327.26, "end": 1329.26, "text": " When you read this again and again."}, {"start": 1329.26, "end": 1331.26, "text": " Then you will speak from your heart."}, {"start": 1331.26, "end": 1333.26, "text": " These very same things."}, {"start": 1333.26, "end": 1335.26, "text": " It becomes."}, {"start": 1335.26, "end": 1337.26, "text": " Emotionalized."}, {"start": 1339.26, "end": 1340.26, "text": " Further."}, {"start": 1340.26, "end": 1343.26, "text": " I should accompany every bead of my japa."}, {"start": 1343.26, "end": 1346.26, "text": " With any one of my heart talks."}, {"start": 1346.26, "end": 1348.26, "text": " Of."}, {"start": 1348.26, "end": 1349.26, "text": " Or bhavanas."}, {"start": 1349.26, "end": 1350.26, "text": " Of."}, {"start": 1350.26, "end": 1351.26, "text": " Vinamrta."}, {"start": 1351.26, "end": 1353.26, "text": " They are all heart talks only."}, {"start": 1353.26, "end": 1354.26, "text": " It's all sound only."}, {"start": 1354.26, "end": 1355.26, "text": " It's all your."}, {"start": 1355.26, "end": 1356.26, "text": " Your conviction."}, {"start": 1356.26, "end": 1357.26, "text": " Your convinced."}, {"start": 1357.26, "end": 1358.26, "text": " And."}, {"start": 1358.26, "end": 1360.26, "text": " Emotionally strong."}, {"start": 1360.26, "end": 1361.26, "text": " Statements."}, {"start": 1361.26, "end": 1363.26, "text": " Of your soul."}, {"start": 1363.26, "end": 1364.26, "text": " Vimrta."}, {"start": 1364.26, "end": 1365.26, "text": " Vinamrta."}, {"start": 1365.26, "end": 1367.26, "text": " So many statements."}, {"start": 1367.26, "end": 1368.26, "text": " That is there."}, {"start": 1368.26, "end": 1373.26, "text": " That is what all the six cards will tell about."}, {"start": 1373.26, "end": 1376.26, "text": " The talk."}, {"start": 1376.26, "end": 1380.26, "text": " That I am insignificant before you."}, {"start": 1380.26, "end": 1381.26, "text": " I possess nothing."}, {"start": 1381.26, "end": 1382.26, "text": " Etc."}, {"start": 1382.26, "end": 1383.26, "text": " Etc."}, {"start": 1383.26, "end": 1384.26, "text": " Like that."}, {"start": 1384.26, "end": 1386.26, "text": " The cards are all meant for instilling this."}, {"start": 1386.26, "end": 1387.26, "text": " Conviction."}, {"start": 1387.26, "end": 1389.26, "text": " Belief."}, {"start": 1389.26, "end": 1390.26, "text": " That you are."}, {"start": 1390.26, "end": 1392.26, "text": " Nothing before God."}, {"start": 1392.26, "end": 1394.26, "text": " God is everything."}, {"start": 1394.26, "end": 1395.26, "text": " That."}, {"start": 1395.26, "end": 1396.26, "text": " That."}, {"start": 1396.26, "end": 1397.26, "text": " Vinamrta."}, {"start": 1397.26, "end": 1401.26, "text": " Feeling."}, {"start": 1401.26, "end": 1403.26, "text": " Are those six cards."}, {"start": 1403.26, "end": 1405.26, "text": " And you go on repeating those."}, {"start": 1405.26, "end": 1409.26, "text": " Reading those cards."}, {"start": 1409.26, "end": 1413.26, "text": " What is that Vinamrta that enters your heart?"}, {"start": 1413.26, "end": 1414.26, "text": " No pain."}, {"start": 1414.26, "end": 1415.26, "text": " No gain."}, {"start": 1415.26, "end": 1416.26, "text": " Your."}, {"start": 1416.26, "end": 1417.26, "text": " Japa."}, {"start": 1417.26, "end": 1418.26, "text": " If you follow these things."}, {"start": 1418.26, "end": 1421.26, "text": " It will become super."}, {"start": 1421.26, "end": 1422.26, "text": " Super."}, {"start": 1422.26, "end": 1424.26, "text": " Even I am trying to follow."}, {"start": 1424.26, "end": 1426.26, "text": " My japa has not become any super."}, {"start": 1426.26, "end": 1429.26, "text": " But I know if you follow this."}, {"start": 1429.26, "end": 1430.26, "text": " It becomes super."}, {"start": 1430.26, "end": 1433.26, "text": " I can write these things."}, {"start": 1433.26, "end": 1435.26, "text": " Because Nama Prabhu is inspiring me."}, {"start": 1435.26, "end": 1437.26, "text": " But to practice these things."}, {"start": 1437.26, "end": 1438.26, "text": " It will take years."}, {"start": 1438.26, "end": 1441.26, "text": " But if you practice these things."}, {"start": 1441.26, "end": 1442.26, "text": " Then."}, {"start": 1442.26, "end": 1446.26, "text": " Where our spiritual consciousness will be."}, {"start": 1446.26, "end": 1452.26, "text": " Hrstam."}, {"start": 1452.26, "end": 1454.26, "text": " Why you should be."}, {"start": 1454.26, "end": 1456.26, "text": " Why you should be."}, {"start": 1456.26, "end": 1458.26, "text": " Happily chanting."}, {"start": 1458.26, "end": 1460.26, "text": " There are reasons."}, {"start": 1460.26, "end": 1461.26, "text": " When you are happy."}, {"start": 1461.26, "end": 1462.26, "text": " There are reasons."}, {"start": 1462.26, "end": 1464.26, "text": " Why you are happy."}, {"start": 1464.26, "end": 1471.26, "text": " So that is intellectualizing."}, {"start": 1471.26, "end": 1474.26, "text": " And then emotionalize."}, {"start": 1474.26, "end": 1477.26, "text": " Intellectualizing is thought."}, {"start": 1477.26, "end": 1478.26, "text": " Thought feeling."}, {"start": 1478.26, "end": 1480.26, "text": " Feeling means emotionalize."}, {"start": 1480.26, "end": 1483.26, "text": " Bhavana means thought feeling."}, {"start": 1484.26, "end": 1488.26, "text": " Thought and feeling."}, {"start": 1488.26, "end": 1491.26, "text": " Just like a person is angry."}, {"start": 1491.26, "end": 1494.26, "text": " Behind anger there is a thought."}, {"start": 1494.26, "end": 1497.26, "text": " So therefore anger is not simply a feeling."}, {"start": 1497.26, "end": 1501.26, "text": " Anger is a thought feeling."}, {"start": 1501.26, "end": 1507.26, "text": " Every emotion is a thought feeling."}, {"start": 1507.26, "end": 1513.26, "text": " That is meaning of Bhavana."}, {"start": 1513.26, "end": 1516.26, "text": " Persona of Shri Nama Prabhu."}, {"start": 1516.26, "end": 1518.26, "text": " My relationship narrative is Preeti."}, {"start": 1518.26, "end": 1523.26, "text": " A respectful intimacy."}, {"start": 1523.26, "end": 1528.26, "text": " Respectful intimacy."}, {"start": 1528.26, "end": 1531.26, "text": " Towards him."}, {"start": 1531.26, "end": 1533.26, "text": " My purpose narrative is serving him."}, {"start": 1533.26, "end": 1536.26, "text": " And receiving his Satchitananda association."}, {"start": 1536.26, "end": 1539.26, "text": " To awaken my love for him."}, {"start": 1539.26, "end": 1541.26, "text": " I should accompany every bead of my japa."}, {"start": 1541.26, "end": 1542.26, "text": " With any one of the heartbeats."}, {"start": 1542.26, "end": 1544.26, "text": " Any one of the heart talks of Bhavana."}, {"start": 1544.26, "end": 1545.26, "text": " See."}, {"start": 1545.26, "end": 1546.26, "text": " When so many Bhavana's you hear."}, {"start": 1546.26, "end": 1547.26, "text": " And you understand."}, {"start": 1547.26, "end": 1550.26, "text": " And you put it in your heart."}, {"start": 1550.26, "end": 1552.26, "text": " Afterward japa becomes."}, {"start": 1552.26, "end": 1554.26, "text": " Sadbhavana japa."}, {"start": 1554.26, "end": 1555.26, "text": " Or soulful japa."}, {"start": 1555.26, "end": 1558.26, "text": " Becomes very easy."}, {"start": 1558.26, "end": 1561.26, "text": " You don't have to indulge your thinking capacity."}, {"start": 1561.26, "end": 1564.26, "text": " To load those Bhavana."}, {"start": 1564.26, "end": 1566.26, "text": " Because so many Bhavana's are there."}, {"start": 1566.26, "end": 1567.26, "text": " Vinamrta."}, {"start": 1567.26, "end": 1568.26, "text": " Rishtam."}, {"start": 1568.26, "end": 1569.26, "text": " On each bead there should be a Bhavana."}, {"start": 1569.26, "end": 1571.26, "text": " Because on each bead Krishna is appearing."}, {"start": 1571.26, "end": 1572.26, "text": " Receiving him with."}, {"start": 1572.26, "end": 1574.26, "text": " Receive him with Bhavana."}, {"start": 1574.26, "end": 1576.26, "text": " Serve him with Bhavana."}, {"start": 1576.26, "end": 1577.26, "text": " Krishna mahlada."}, {"start": 1577.26, "end": 1578.26, "text": " Utsaha."}, {"start": 1578.26, "end": 1579.26, "text": " Sambandha."}, {"start": 1579.26, "end": 1580.26, "text": " Atma Jnana."}, {"start": 1580.26, "end": 1581.26, "text": " Sharanagati."}, {"start": 1581.26, "end": 1582.26, "text": " Kripa Apeksha."}, {"start": 1582.26, "end": 1583.26, "text": " Ashraya Apeksha."}, {"start": 1583.26, "end": 1584.26, "text": " Reksha."}, {"start": 1584.26, "end": 1585.26, "text": " Bharata Pratra."}, {"start": 1585.26, "end": 1587.26, "text": " Krithanya Arpanam."}, {"start": 1587.26, "end": 1589.26, "text": " Kshama Apeksha."}, {"start": 1589.26, "end": 1591.26, "text": " Seva Apeksha."}, {"start": 1591.26, "end": 1593.26, "text": " And Vairagya perceptions of."}, {"start": 1593.26, "end": 1594.26, "text": " Self."}, {"start": 1594.26, "end": 1595.26, "text": " Of Nirahankara."}, {"start": 1595.26, "end": 1596.26, "text": " Nirmama."}, {"start": 1596.26, "end": 1597.26, "text": " Nisahaya."}, {"start": 1597.26, "end": 1598.26, "text": " Niswartha."}, {"start": 1598.26, "end": 1600.26, "text": " And Nir Apeksha."}, {"start": 1601.26, "end": 1608.26, "text": " Now these are all the things that are explained in the rest of the cards."}, {"start": 1608.26, "end": 1611.26, "text": " So take for instance Vinamrta."}, {"start": 1611.26, "end": 1614.26, "text": " Let's say six seven cards are there."}, {"start": 1614.26, "end": 1618.26, "text": " So once all those six seven cards you read repeatedly and then."}, {"start": 1618.26, "end": 1623.26, "text": " Feel for it."}, {"start": 1623.26, "end": 1625.26, "text": " Then."}, {"start": 1625.26, "end": 1628.26, "text": " Vinamrta feeling."}, {"start": 1628.26, "end": 1630.26, "text": " Will automatically come."}, {"start": 1631.26, "end": 1636.26, "text": " You don't have to bring all those six cards."}, {"start": 1636.26, "end": 1638.26, "text": " Something of that will."}, {"start": 1638.26, "end": 1641.26, "text": " Come into the surface."}, {"start": 1641.26, "end": 1644.26, "text": " So much abundant feelings you have."}, {"start": 1644.26, "end": 1645.26, "text": " Six."}, {"start": 1645.26, "end": 1647.26, "text": " Out of that one will understand."}, {"start": 1647.26, "end": 1650.26, "text": " Vinamrta."}, {"start": 1650.26, "end": 1652.26, "text": " So what does Vinamrta mean?"}, {"start": 1652.26, "end": 1658.26, "text": " That is the first thing you should understand by reading those cards."}, {"start": 1658.26, "end": 1660.26, "text": " Go on hearing that."}, {"start": 1660.26, "end": 1662.26, "text": " Then automatically that will."}, {"start": 1662.26, "end": 1663.26, "text": " That meaning will."}, {"start": 1663.26, "end": 1669.26, "text": " For instance Krishna is source of everything."}, {"start": 1669.26, "end": 1670.26, "text": " I do not possess anything."}, {"start": 1670.26, "end": 1673.26, "text": " I do not own anything."}, {"start": 1673.26, "end": 1677.26, "text": " Everything that I have is given by him."}, {"start": 1677.26, "end": 1679.26, "text": " Now this is an intellectual truth."}, {"start": 1679.26, "end": 1682.26, "text": " It's a true intellectual fact."}, {"start": 1682.26, "end": 1686.26, "text": " But as you go on telling this intellectual fact."}, {"start": 1686.26, "end": 1688.26, "text": " What will happen?"}, {"start": 1688.26, "end": 1691.26, "text": " Feeling also will come."}, {"start": 1691.26, "end": 1694.26, "text": " Is it not?"}, {"start": 1694.26, "end": 1696.26, "text": " I did not possess anything."}, {"start": 1696.26, "end": 1699.26, "text": " The feeling that Krishna is a possessor Bhagavan of everything."}, {"start": 1699.26, "end": 1701.26, "text": " Feeling also will come."}, {"start": 1701.26, "end": 1706.26, "text": " So go on repeating this content in these cards."}, {"start": 1706.26, "end": 1709.26, "text": " Both intellectually and emotionally."}, {"start": 1709.26, "end": 1711.26, "text": " You will see that."}, {"start": 1711.26, "end": 1716.26, "text": " They become part of your subconscious."}, {"start": 1716.26, "end": 1724.26, "text": " It is part of your relationship with Namaprabhu."}, {"start": 1724.26, "end": 1727.26, "text": " So this is the golden secret card."}, {"start": 1727.26, "end": 1730.26, "text": " At least this secret card."}, {"start": 1730.26, "end": 1732.26, "text": " Till next Ekadashi."}, {"start": 1732.26, "end": 1734.26, "text": " Please all of you."}, {"start": 1734.26, "end": 1739.26, "text": " Take a copy of this."}, {"start": 1739.26, "end": 1743.26, "text": " From Indrapati."}, {"start": 1743.26, "end": 1744.26, "text": " And."}, {"start": 1744.26, "end": 1750.26, "text": " Just understand."}, {"start": 1750.26, "end": 1752.26, "text": " Later on we will go into."}, {"start": 1752.26, "end": 1755.26, "text": " What is Vinamruta and law."}, {"start": 1755.26, "end": 1756.26, "text": " Step by step."}, {"start": 1756.26, "end": 1759.26, "text": " What are the three secrets."}, {"start": 1759.26, "end": 1761.26, "text": " Hear and chant."}, {"start": 1761.26, "end": 1764.26, "text": " Hear your chant."}, {"start": 1764.26, "end": 1765.26, "text": " Then."}, {"start": 1765.26, "end": 1768.26, "text": " Task hearing over hearing."}, {"start": 1768.26, "end": 1772.26, "text": " Pile up hearing over hearing."}, {"start": 1772.26, "end": 1773.26, "text": " Then."}, {"start": 1773.26, "end": 1774.26, "text": " You will see."}, {"start": 1774.26, "end": 1776.26, "text": " Unlimited ways of relating with the Namaprabhu is there."}, {"start": 1776.26, "end": 1778.26, "text": " By heart talk."}, {"start": 1778.26, "end": 1785.26, "text": " At least one heart talk should be there in each japa."}, {"start": 1785.26, "end": 1788.26, "text": " That means your background is also completely involved in."}, {"start": 1788.26, "end": 1789.26, "text": " Beat after beat."}, {"start": 1789.26, "end": 1790.26, "text": " Beat after beat."}, {"start": 1790.26, "end": 1794.26, "text": " Beat after beat."}, {"start": 1794.26, "end": 1798.26, "text": " Minimum heart talk is Shraddha."}, {"start": 1798.26, "end": 1800.26, "text": " So next 15 days."}, {"start": 1800.26, "end": 1801.26, "text": " Till next Ekadashi."}, {"start": 1801.26, "end": 1802.26, "text": " Practice Shraddha."}, {"start": 1802.26, "end": 1808.26, "text": " So first six cards of Shraddha also you can practice."}, {"start": 1808.26, "end": 1809.26, "text": " Or you can go slow."}, {"start": 1809.26, "end": 1812.26, "text": " First practice these three things."}, {"start": 1812.26, "end": 1814.26, "text": " Golden card for next."}, {"start": 1814.26, "end": 1816.26, "text": " Till next Ekadashi."}, {"start": 1816.26, "end": 1821.26, "text": " Then the next Ekadashi when I do or whenever next Japa Yajna I do."}, {"start": 1821.26, "end": 1826.26, "text": " I will talk about the six cards of Shraddha."}, {"start": 1826.26, "end": 1827.26, "text": " And the next Ekadashi."}, {"start": 1827.26, "end": 1828.26, "text": " Each Ekadashi."}, {"start": 1828.26, "end": 1831.26, "text": " I will deal with one one Bhavana."}, {"start": 1831.26, "end": 1843.7, "text": " So, we are going deeper into soulful japa."}]}